member.summary:
Draws the area of a Control.
An easy way to use for debugging is by adding it to the Control's Draw event.
eg. control.Draw += control.DrawDebug;

member.example:
For example:\n In a mod assembly called MyMod.dll
public static string MyPath => GetModImagePath("ui/reward_screen/card_transform_reward.png")
results in MyPath = "res://MyMod/images/ui/reward_screen/card_transform_reward.png"

